Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:21.59,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}踊りだす
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:26.89,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}焼きついたように色づいた風景は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:31.02,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fs30\pos(700,668)}と
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:31.02,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}転んだくらいじゃ融けないから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:32.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}世界は続くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:37.11,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fs30\pos(425,668)}はかな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:37.11,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}儚いままの今を抱きしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:45.07,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}変わらないまま時間と　光見つめて歩いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:46.27,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}奔跑向前的日子里 我所到达的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.47,0:02:50.90,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}推开门
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:56.53,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}星空的彼方 梦的足迹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:03:00.57,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}让我们拾起攒积放声歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:06.37,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}梦所到达的地方 至今仍藏心底
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:11.75,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}包裹夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:16.17,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}施起魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:21.59,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}跳出舞蹈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:26.89,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}燃烧似的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:31.02,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}只是摔一跤的话不会融化消失
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:32.81,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}世界还在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:37.11,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}拥抱不确定的现在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:45.07,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}与亘古不变的时间 循着光 迈向前
